<div class="ui bulleted list">
  <div class="item">Save: to save any changes made of the student record direct to the backend database.</div>
  <div class="item">Undo: to rollback one recent change made to the student record.</div>
  <div class="item">First Record: brings the data in the first student in the database and display it on the screen.</div>
  <div class="item">Previous Record: to bring and show the data of the previous students from the students’ database that is sorted by the student number.</div>
  <div class="item">Next Record: to bring and show the data of the next students from the students’ database that is sorted by the student number.</div>
  <div class="item">Last Records: brings the data in the last student in the database and display it on the screen.</div>
  <div class="item">All: display a list of all students exist in the database, along with an appropriate button to go back to the single data entry view.</div>
  <div class="item">Find Record: search the students’ database to retrieve an individual student information based on a given student number.</div>
</div>
